    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable door dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a few minor scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though the suspension is starting to feel a bit loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It has been regularly maintained, but expect the typical wear and tear associated with a well-used vehicle.",
      "price": 18500.0,
