      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person. It's in such incredible shape that it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car, keeping it spotless and making sure it runs like a dream. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but I'm ready to pass it on to someone who will love it just as much. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
