    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 platform, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated double VANOS system for optimal volumetric efficiency. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is exceptional, having undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a complete suspension refresh with OEM bushings to maintain factory kinematics. The engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, and the critical rod bearing service has been documented. With a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior, this specimen offers the tactile, analog feedback and mechanical purity that defines the M-division's golden era.",
